WEBVTT

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:32.736
I never paid attention to studying,
and because of this very reason,

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:35.760
I would end up hurting people close to me.

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:39.920
Everyone in my family was
very well-educated

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:44.096
so they wanted me to do well in studies
and become something too.

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:46.336
To fulfill their wish,

00:01:46.360 --> 00:01:51.216
I joined a course in Masters
of Computer Application,

00:01:51.240 --> 00:01:54.960
but to me it was torture
rather than an education.

00:01:55.960 --> 00:02:00.456
And often I would bunk classes
to sit in the library